
Awal-w n tujma

Jjmeɣ lehduṛ di tteffɣen imi-m
Jjmeɣ taḍsa n wudem-im
Imi ffeṛqen-aɣ lebḥuṛ

Tecbiḍ lḥeb deg uclim
Tufrareḍ-d gar tulawin
Tsenna-ḍ tayri-w d aɛemmuṛ

Taḍsa n tiṭ-im d ccefṛ-im
Akked nnecṛaḥa n wul-im
Am tala war ǧin neqquṛ

Mennaɣ ad kem qqneɣ d abzim
Ad zuxxeɣ s yisem-im
Ad yassem wucbiḥ di zzeṛzur
